      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A. Because any computation can be rewritten as\narithmetic over a field, and any arithmetic relation can\nbe enforced using just multiplication of linear\nexpressions.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A. Because any computation can be rewritten as arithmetic over a field, and any arithmetic relation can be enforced using just multiplication of linear expressions.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
