      "text": "➤ Boolean constraint\n\n\nEnforce:\nb . (b - 1) = 0\n\n👉 fits R1CS",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "hJAEf2tukQjTnRtdL6b37",
      "originalText": "➤ Boolean constraint\n\n\nEnforce:\nb . (b - 1) = 0\n\n👉 fits R1CS",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "UvLlSdy2nxJEOgcrd5Z_I",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 7111.502345064425,
      "y": 1828.5811448032491,
