      "updated": 1775122279992,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Putting all constraints \ntogether as matrices:\n\nA, B, C\n\nFor this eg:\nA = [0, 1, 0, 0]\n     [1, 0, 0, 0]\n\nB = [0, 1, 0, 0]\n     [3, 0, 1, 0]\n\nC = [0, 0, 1, 0]\n     [0, 0, 0, 1]\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Putting all constraints \ntogether as matrices:\n\nA, B, C\n\nFor this eg:\nA = [0, 1, 0, 0]\n     [1, 0, 0, 0]\n\nB = [0, 1, 0, 0]\n     [3, 0, 1, 0]\n\nC = [0, 0, 1, 0]\n     [0, 0, 0, 1]\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
