    {
      "id": "1wTqo7rIw5Bq-F8t938wE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4650.623627769457,
      "y": 2994.94291992471,
      "width": 664.51953125,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 211595105,
      "version": 487,
      "versionNonce": 133080751,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775123024313,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Let's plug in the witness values & check that each constraint holds.\n\npick some actual value for x.\nSay:\nx = 5\n\nThen:\n\nt = x^2 = 25\ny = t + 3 = 28\n\nSo, the witness vector becomes:\nw = [1, 5, 25, 28]",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Let's plug in the witness values & check that each constraint holds.\n\npick some actual value for x.\nSay:\nx = 5\n\nThen:\n\nt = x^2 = 25\ny = t + 3 = 28\n\nSo, the witness vector becomes:\nw = [1, 5, 25, 28]",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0CBsl3ZjeROasOoPfwtTZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4652.98688570593,
      "y": 3347.1963509711236,
      "width": 166.57192993164062,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1264894305,
