      "text": "Compute:\nA . w = [1, 0, 0, 0] . [1, 5, 25, 28] = 1 . 1 + 0 . 5 + 0 . 25 + 0 . 28 = 1\n\nB . w = [3, 0, 1, 0] . [1, 5, 25, 28] = 3 . 1 + 0 . 5 + 1 . 25 + 0 . 28 = 28\n\nC . w = [0, 0, 0, 1] . [1, 5, 25, 28] = 0 . 1 + 0 . 5 + 0 . 25 + 1 . 28 = 28\n",
