      "text": "Will get to this 👇",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "8jO3W2Eg-hh5mSRqIqYPx",
      "originalText": "Will get to this 👇",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bUBkUcARqRx-drRdv6u0G",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4638.58093866003,
      "y": 3790.1351434433764,
      "width": 340.3242703465876,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "eTm1seG_09_aU_JSQq6FX"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1019264271,
      "version": 50,
      "versionNonce": 6997647,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "8jO3W2Eg-hh5mSRqIqYPx",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775123763965,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "So what did you achieve?\n\nYou proved that the witness\n\nw = [1,5,25,28]\n\nsatisfies both constraints, which\nmeans it is a valid execution of:\n\ny = x^2 + 3",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "So what did you achieve?\n\nYou proved that the witness\n\nw = [1,5,25,28]\n\nsatisfies both constraints, which means it is a valid execution of:\n\ny = x^2 + 3",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
