      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🧠 Mental model\n\nA zk circuit is:\n\nA set of polynomial equations over a finite field\n\nNOT:\n• if/else (no branching directly)\n• loops (must be unrolled)\n• dynamic memory",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "tLh0OG0TMS8aDcRvvoi1F",
      "originalText": "🧠 Mental model\n\nA zk circuit is:\n\nA set of polynomial equations over a finite field\n\nNOT:\n• if/else (no branching directly)\n• loops (must be unrolled)\n• dynamic memory",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
